The '''Bukalla''' is an entity exclusively alluded to in [[Dagannoth Supreme]]'s examine text.<ref>The examine reads: "The dagannoth king responsible for the death of the Bukalla."</ref> Although initially planned to be a lost tribe of vikings vanquished by Dagannoth Supreme,{{CiteGeneral |url=https://www.reddit.com/r/2007scape/comments/4hha91/i_used_to_work_on_rs_ask_me_selected_things/d2pqszd/?context=10000 |title=I used to work on RS, Ask Me Selected Things? |author=Mod James |date=3 May 2016 |accessdate=October 6 2018 |publisher=Reddit |archiveurl=http://archive.is/38sui |archivedate= October 6 2018 |quote=This is another example of me dropping something I could come back to later on - I had no specific plans, but I was more leaning towards it being a 'lost tribe' of vikings than an individual. Obviously someone else went somewhere else with that though XD}} the Bukalla eventually turned out to be a legendary [[Fremennik]] warrior.

